         DeepResearch.<b>Se<span class="sl">/</span>rver</b> feature — they run on this site's server.</p>`
      : `<b>Introspection mode.</b> I can read my own source code — ask how I'm built,
         or name a file like <code>src/pipeline.js</code>.
